@startuml
[*] --> Requested
Requested --> RecipientsLoaded : load class/student recipients
RecipientsLoaded --> Failed : no recipients
RecipientsLoaded --> BotTokenResolved : load system bot token
BotTokenResolved --> ResolvingRecipient : for each recipient
BotTokenResolved --> Failed : bot unavailable
ResolvingRecipient --> FailedRecipient : no active class/guild/user id
ResolvingRecipient --> SendingDM : user id resolved
SendingDM --> SentRecipient : Discord send succeeds
SendingDM --> FailedRecipient : Discord send fails
SentRecipient --> Aggregating
FailedRecipient --> Aggregating
Aggregating --> Completed : delivery summary returned
Completed --> [*]
Failed --> [*]
@enduml
